Package: ibaq4diann
Title: iBAQ Calculation from DIA-NN Proteomics Reports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alison Felipe Alencar Chaves", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alison.chaves@example.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Computes intensity-Based Absolute Quantification (iBAQ) values
    from DIA-NN search results (report.parquet files) and a reference proteome
    FASTA. Implements the iBAQ method of Schwanhausser et al. (2011)
    <doi:10.1038/nature10098>, including in-silico tryptic digestion, quality
    filtering of DIA-NN reports, and flexible output formats. Also provides
    plotting utilities for visualising protein abundance ranks, distributions,
    sample correlations, and dynamic range.
